message: "If you use the ESF Companion, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "ESF Companion"
abstract: >-
  A lightweight, domain-agnostic version of the Epistemic Stewardship Framework
  for maintaining intellectual ownership in AI-assisted work. Five practices:
  Position Statement, Five Questions, Records of Resistance, AI Use Log, and
  Disclosure. Works with any AI tool, any discipline, any project.
